OL,3,GOPINIONCITV sale: what once would've
OL,4,Cbeen considered unthinkable now
OL,5,Cregarded as a rescue deal
OL,6,
OL,7,FNot so long ago the thought of ITV
OL,8,Fbeing in foreign ownership would have
OL,9,Fbeen simply unthinkable.
OL,11,FThe thought of ITV being owned by Sky `
OL,12,Fin turn owned by the US company Comcast
OL,13,F` would have been unpalatable to
OL,14,Fregulators.
OL,16,FITV and Sky together would simply have
OL,17,Fbeen thought too powerful, controlling
OL,18,Fsome 70pc of the TV advertising market.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
