OL,3,GOPINIONCITV sale: what once would've
OL,4,Cbeen considered unthinkable now
OL,5,Cregarded as a rescue deal
OL,6,
OL,7,FThe idea of ITV ` the nation's
OL,8,Fprincipal free-to-air commercial
OL,9,Fbroadcaster ` being ultimately in
OL,10,Fforeign hands would have aroused huge
OL,11,Fpolitical controversy.
OL,13,FBut there was little outrage when news
OL,14,Fof a possible #1.6bn deal to sell ITV's
OL,15,Fchannels and ITV X to Sky emerged on
OL,16,FFriday.
OL,18,FRather, some described it as a rescue
OL,19,Fdeal.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
