OL,3,GOPINIONCITV sale: what once would've
OL,4,Cbeen considered unthinkable now
OL,5,Cregarded as a rescue deal
OL,6,
OL,7,FIt seems like another world for those
OL,8,Fof us old enough to remember when the
OL,9,FIBA wanted regional shareholders and
OL,10,Ftried to ensure that registered offices
OL,11,Fwere within regional franchise areas.
OL,13,FThe challenges facing commercial
OL,14,Fbroadcasters are huge. Falling ratings
OL,15,Fand falling linear advertising almost
OL,16,Fseem to be creating a vicious circle.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
