OL,3,GOPINIONCITV sale: what once would've
OL,4,Cbeen considered unthinkable now
OL,5,Cregarded as a rescue deal
OL,6,
OL,7,FThere can be no certainty that this
OL,8,Fdeal will actually happen. There is no
OL,9,Fpoint speculating just now on exactly
OL,10,Fwhat it may mean for viewers and the
OL,11,Fchannel line-up.
OL,13,FBut there are two key regulatory
OL,14,Fquestions.
OL,16,FOne is the role of the Competition and
OL,17,FMarkets Authority. Will it allow the
OL,18,Fdeal? Or will it insist on certain
OL,19,Fsafeguards?
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
