OL,3,GOPINIONCITV sale: what once would've
OL,4,Cbeen considered unthinkable now
OL,5,Cregarded as a rescue deal
OL,6,
OL,7,FITV is still tied by undertakings given
OL,8,Fwhen ITV plc was formed to help prevent
OL,9,Fit from becoming too powerful in the
OL,10,Fadvertising market. Oh the irony.
OL,12,FThe other concerns the role of Ofcom.
OL,13,FCan it ensure that public service
OL,14,Fcommitments and the broad investment in
OL,15,Fthe schedule are maintained?
OL,17,FBut let's take stock.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
