OL,3,GOPINIONCITV sale: what once would've
OL,4,Cbeen considered unthinkable now
OL,5,Cregarded as a rescue deal
OL,6,
OL,7,FITV would ultimately be owned by an
OL,8,FAmerican company Comcast. Channel 5 is
OL,9,Falready owned by Paramount. They are
OL,10,Fthe British branches of multinationals.
OL,12,FA few years ago I looked at the
OL,13,Farguments made by some who wanted to
OL,14,Fprotect Channel 4 from privatisation.
OL,16,FTheir deep concern was genuine but they
OL,17,Fseemed to have lost sight of the fact
OL,18,Fthat modern Channel 4 looks and feels
OL,19,Ftoo much like other commercial
OL,20,Fchannels. They used the language of art
OL,21,Fand culture to defend schlock.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
