OL,3,GOPINIONCITV sale: what once would've
OL,4,Cbeen considered unthinkable now
OL,5,Cregarded as a rescue deal
OL,6,
OL,7,FIf this deal goes through, there will
OL,8,Fbe a principled argument for keeping
OL,9,FChannel 4 in public ownership ` at
OL,10,Fleast it will still be in British
OL,11,Fhands.
OL,13,FMuch more importantly, we must never
OL,14,Ftake the BBC for granted.
OL,16,FI'm glad the corporation is once again
OL,17,Freminding viewers that its programmes
OL,18,Fare only possible because of the unique
OL,19,Fway it is paid for.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
