OL,3,GOPINIONCITV sale: what once would've
OL,4,Cbeen considered unthinkable now
OL,5,Cregarded as a rescue deal
OL,6,
OL,7,FOr it might be about a commercial
OL,8,Fchannel's relationship with its
OL,9,Fcustomers and shareholders.
OL,11,FDesperate times call for desperate
OL,12,Fmeasures. But ITV cannot simply become
OL,13,Fpart of the British division of a
OL,14,Fmultinational based overseas.
OL,16,FOfcom and the CMA need to ensure
OL,17,Fsafeguards for the public before this
OL,18,Fdeal can go through.
